Time travel 2D puzzle platformer By: Quantastic Team
Quantastic is simple, yet interesting new 2D puzzle platformer game that revolves around time travel. By reaching portals, you progress through beautifully designed levels and carefully devised puzzles. Game features light and shadows effects as well as realistic physics simulation of your character's enviroment.
